<h2 id="guidelines">Guidelines</h2>
<h3 id="avoid-bloat">Avoid CSS bloat</h3>
<p>Use these classes to avoid writing and maintaining unnecessary styles that do what these classes already do. In many cases you can implement a feature without writing any CSS by leveraging these shortcuts!</p>
<h3 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h3>
<p>There are no accessibility recommendations for these classes.</p>
